It seems you have barely enough memory to run a vanilla copy of KSP, never mind one with mods,  you should really have  a paging file with that little amount of memory, this is a section of hard drive that is used when the RAM is overwhelmed.        Which sadly for you, especially if you have any other apps running at the same time , means all the time.
